          HS/Link is a high speed, full streaming, bidirectional, batch
          file transfer protocol with advanced Full-Streaming-Error-
          Correction.  Each side of the link is allowed to provide a list
          of files to be sent.  Files will be sent in BOTH directions until
          both sides of the link are satisfied.

          HS/Link is not just another bidirectional protocol, it is also a
          very fast protocol for normal downloading and uploading,
          incorporating some new ideas (such as Full-Streaming-Error-
          Correction and Dynamic-Code-Substitution) to make things happen a
          bit faster and with greater reliability.

          This program is not free!  You are hereby licensed to use this
          program for a trial period of 30 days free of charge.  If, after
          30 days, you decide that you would like to continue using HSLINK,
