          Registration removes the "UNREGISTERED" message and also enables
          a bar-graphic display of file transfer status, an estimation of
          remaining time to transfer each file, and a calculation of
          combined thruput during bidirectional transfers.

          Please feel free to distribute HSLINK to your friends and local
